You'll be dead.

10
00:00:19,913 --> 00:00:21,398
My boss made a call.

11
00:00:21,520 --> 00:00:23,230
You told Mayor Lindsay.

12
00:00:25,628 --> 00:00:28,982
We have to be careful.
We can't fall in love.

13
